Subject: Apply Backend Updates - Fail to Apply
Description:
Checking for backend updates completes successfuly. System provides list of available updates for installation.

When attempting to apply backend updates to the system, "Applying Backend Updates" status message appears, however installation never completes, system never updates, and eventually web console times out.
Solution_Comment__c: Closing as resolved as I was able to update the key on the backend to get the new updates.
